			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1470200">
									

<p>I think it has a lot to do with the fact that he has a long history outside the Foundation, and that he can be crossed over with a load of other items and will both make sense and be unique in how they're portrayed. It opens up the playing field for what you can do with the character, which gets the creative juices flowing. Gives people something new and fun to play with, something outside of the Foundation.</p>
